<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="19Feb1939"><font color="red">19 February 1939</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): Many thanks for &hellip; the further corrected galleys he found of Part IV episode IV &hellip; I shall be greatly and undeservedly honoured if Mr Joyce does finally send me the advance copy he received on his birthday, with corrections made on it, though not in his own hand </div>
